19
00:04:22.362 --> 00:04:23.765
<i>This is Penny.</i>

20
00:04:23.898 --> 00:04:25.365
<i>Sorry I missed you.</i>
<i>Please leave a message.</i>

21
00:04:25.499 --> 00:04:26.801
<i>and I'll circle</i>
